San Onofre is my old stomping ground...but pretty far away from LA  
depending on what part you're staying in. It is on the most southern  
end of the Orange Curtain.

Just North of LA you have Zuma beach and all up and down PCH pretty  
much any state beach park will have plenty of VeeDubs.


